---
import Collapsible from './Collapsible.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10">
  <Collapsible number="01" title="About" defaultOpen={true}>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
      I'm a Solutions Architect based in Nashville with 18+ years in enterprise IT, focused on
      Large Enterprise, Federal, and other public-sector environments. My work sits at the
      intersection of infrastructure and analytics — designing AI-ready cloud platforms while
      also building the Python pipelines, statistical models, and dashboards that turn raw data
      into decisions. I'm currently completing a Master of Science in Analytics at Georgia Tech,
      with coursework in machine learning, NLP, and statistical modeling.
    </p>
  </Collapsible>
</section>
